{
  "type": "page",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### Condition Builder Formula (E3)\n\n以下演示 condition-builder 的 `formulas` / `formulaForIf` runtime 消费（E3 收口）。当 `formulas.enabled=true` 时，条件项右侧切换为表达式值槽（`data-slot=\"condition-formula-value\"`），可输入 Flux 表达式串。当 `formulaForIf.enabled=true` 时，组级 `if` 输入标注为可求值表达式。"
    },
    {
      "type": "form",
      "id": "condition-formula-test-form",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "condition-builder",
          "name": "formulaConditions",
          "label": "Formula 值槽（formulas.enabled + formula seed）",
          "embed": true,
          "builderMode": "full",
          "showAndOr": true,
          "showNot": true,
          "showIf": true,
          "formulas": {
            "enabled": true,
            "formula": "'defaultExpr'"
          },
          "formulaForIf": {
            "enabled": true
          },
          "fields": [
            { "name": "name", "label": "名称", "type": "text", "placeholder": "输入名称" },
            { "name": "age", "label": "年龄", "type": "number" },
            {
              "name": "status",
              "label": "状态",
              "type": "select",
              "options": [
                { "label": "活跃", "value": "active" },
                { "label": "停用", "value": "inactive" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "condition-builder",
          "name": "literalConditions",
          "label": "字面量值槽（formulas 缺省，无回归基线）",
          "embed": true,
          "builderMode": "full",
          "showAndOr": true,
          "fields": [
            { "name": "title", "label": "标题", "type": "text" },
            { "name": "count", "label": "数量", "type": "number" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
